tive medicine  creation of the Center for Outcomes Research  collaboration with OSF HealthCare in the creation of the Jump Trading Simulation   Education Center  construction of a new anatomy lab and classrooms  and the recent transition to a four year medical school She has served as Governor for the Illinois downstate chapter of the largest medical specialty organization in the U S  physician mentor  and skilled educator and clinician Dr  Rusch is married to Dr  Thomas Cusack  Professor of Radiology at UICOMP  She is mother to seven children and grandmother to eleven UICOMP Documents Strategic Plan Annual Report Bylaws Standing Committees and Special Committees About Regional Dean Fast Facts More About the Region Visiting the Campus Contact Us About Education Research Patient Care Departments News Giving INFORMATION FOR  Prospective Students Current Students Faculty   Staff Alumni   Friends Patients RESOURCES  UIC Directory Blackboard Event Calendar Emergency Information Contact Us Apply Now Give Contact Us If you have questions  comments  or problems accessing this site  please E mail the webmaster College of Medicine Chicago Peoria Rockford Urbana 